      • setFormat

        public Labels setFormat(String format)
        Sets the format string for an axis label. Defaults to "{value}".
        Parameters:
        format - the new format string. Use "{value}" as a placeholder for the axis value.
        See Also:
        http://api.highcharts.com/highstock#xAxis.labels.format
